snippet.title: Best VGM 628 - Ace Combat 6 - The Liberation of Gracemeria
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360
Ace Combat 6 : Fires of Liberation (2007)
The Liberation of Gracemeria
Keiki Kobayashi
